The paper discusses interactive knowledge base debugging, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and involves logical reasoning and query generation. The paper also involves mathematical analysis of query selection measures, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The use of logical knowledge bases also suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the user experience and understandability of generated queries, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
